{
  "id": "RAW_45ee32a4",
  "title": "用了上百款 AI 产品后，我终于想不起没有 AI 的日子是怎么过的了",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mjc1NjM3MjY2MA==&mid=2691563748&idx=1&sn=572a191f9ee20103fb5431e522ee521e",
  "date": "2026-01-15 10:24:00",
  "author": "腾讯科技",
  "siteName": "腾讯科技",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.34782608695652173\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1035\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100008096\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0d446e1d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FxVMwH6zrFw54QIgPlu7lH2HDYCRPkEOciaM8JJkBCXiboKfQytvT9tuyON1RibwYXPojibz1DNNFsgU12FYAsNuc7g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">「编者按」：以定力致远，以重构图新。大象新闻、大象财富联合腾讯新闻、腾讯科技推出2025年终策划《定力与重构》，回望2025、展望2026，让洞察照见本质，向变革寻求确定。本篇内容由四木相对论撰写。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: right;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">文 | 四木相对论</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: right;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">编辑 | 博阳</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">有朋友曾在2025年初问我，这一年的AI行业会有什么巨变？我的回答是：我更想知道它将如何改变我的生活。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">当时这样回答的原因是，能用到的AI产品种类太少，而且除了 ChatGPT，能打的实在不多。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">没想到一年后的今天，AI真的“长进了”我的生活。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">我不再只是对话框里琢磨 Prompt，而是习惯把深奥或琐碎的问题抛给 AI 助手；遇到需要深度研究的话题，我会先用 Agent 或 DeepResearch 查资料，看报告；想到什么 idea，我会对着 AI 语音输入法即兴表达，由它来负责润色；甚至在深夜，我会看着那只毛茸茸的AI宠物，想从它的眼睛里读到一点陪伴感。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">如果真的统计我在这一年用过的 AI 产品，估计得有上百个。</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6194444444444445\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=93be5c92&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FxVMwH6zrFw64OLutUic6obicqeTsBGGZL3CJ1DjcSklD3bjECL1ZjrWpc21ficnH4TLmm1VWO35C2S3e9QdnGFf3w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: normal;\">*2025年我用过的一部分产品</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">当然，我也感受到现在的 AI 称不上完美。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">比如 AI 宠物是否在线会受限于网络配置；AI 助手给到的文案还挺机械；AI 生成的视频依然免不了崩坏需要抽卡；AI 眼镜的功能还会受制于超级巨头的生态；甚至，很多 AI Agent 依旧完成不了任务。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但即便如此，短短一年，我的生活确实因为还不够完美的 AI 发生了很多变化。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 20px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);font-weight: bold;\">01</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 20px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);font-weight: bold;\">被AI改变的365天</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这一年之所以能折腾这么产品，还是</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">因为 AI 应用进入了质变期。这种变化不只在于产品数量的井喷，更因为效果的提升和交互颗粒度的细化。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">感触最深的，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">首先是通用 AI 助手对生活的改造。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">2025年几乎所有的通用 AI 助手的都进一步丰富了自己的垂直功能。尤其是 ChatGPT、Gemini、豆包、元宝、千问这几款，囊括了图像、视频、文字、语音全模态，把日常的查询、翻译、文案修改、P图、学习等需求安排得明明白白。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">而且，这几个产品各有绝活。ChatGPT 靠着持续优化的记忆功能，成了我打开次数最多的 AI 助手。我会经常和它对话，让它帮我分析自己和他人的想法。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">而 Gemini 在接入 Google 最强图像处理模型 NanoBanana 后，成为帮我处理图片最多的产品。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">至于豆包、元宝和千问，它们的优势在于懂中文、功能全、响应快。2025年这几款产品的多模态能力提升非常明显。所以直接对着它们下指令已经成了我的习惯。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">像刚过去的圣诞，我邀请了 AI 行业的朋友小聚，就直接用豆包操盘了视觉设计，不过十分钟就整完了邀请海报。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"2\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.77734375\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1536\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100008094\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a0adc71c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FxVMwH6zrFw64OLutUic6obicqeTsBGGZL3bQh0eZPUcwpmNXqgtQ11Y73jvRz8ueyTqk8bAwO8ibKqAIfpN8Ix8EQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: normal;\">*豆包生成，让它把我的形象也贴进海报，非常丝滑</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">临近年底，AI 输入法又全面接管了我的表达。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">它的奇妙之处在于，语音输入法接入大模型，不仅提升了识别准确度，还加入了理解和整理能力。就算是一段语焉不详的话，它也能分分钟梳理明白。这对打字手残星人实在太过友好，我开始习惯拿着手机“口喷”一切。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.0595903165735567\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1074\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100008093\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e071e040&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FxVMwH6zrFw64OLutUic6obicqeTsBGGZL3Zueibbg6rgdJYnsd9nIMOJQ2GFyDRSQQEYa8eT1IYltPdHjGGeRBm9A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: normal;\">*左图：微信输入法语音转文字的内容；右图：“问AI”一键整理后的内容</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">生活之外，我的工作也被 AI 重塑了大半。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">2025年，DeepReasearch 和进化版的 Coding 产品是必备工具。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">先是 DeepResearch。自从海外产品发布后，很多AI助手都内置了这一功能。现在面对陌生课题，先用 DeepResearch 收集并整理网络信息，能帮我快速了解信息。</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5468025949953661\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1079\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bd494aee&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FxVMwH6zrFw64OLutUic6obicqeTsBGGZL3LKhSjX4V3AMWPqpKcHOwdCnxicZwsE7YCsPjicNrL3fkG59dd3zjW6Rg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5468025949953661\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1079\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f28d359e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FxVMwH6zrFw64OLutUic6obicqeTsBGGZL32u8qB9ueZBa5Ae0h13Eq3bjSAKwBBuVY1DZv77pS4WUGUduujnSUzg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: normal;\">*用ChatGPT和Gemini的DeepResearch做调研，用IMA管理和查询个人知识库</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">DeepResearch 出的结果可以一键导出成 PDF 存下来，连同一些关键的网页整理存放在 IMA 上。要用的时候不再需要我手动查找，直接在 IMA 里@个人知识库，输入要查询的关键词，就能找到相关内容并进行总结。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">IMA 还打通了腾讯生态，可以放高质量的公众号文章，整体挺方便。</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6765327695560254\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"946\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=17ce6b03&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FxVMwH6zrFw64OLutUic6obicqeTsBGGZL3vxBvELFNH46Owt3VlXmxfNzlRXW8rbviaWkKhcXjNDBTfKYrK45fhAQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: normal;\">*用IMA管理和查询个人知识库</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">为了提升工作效率，这一年我还 Vibe Coding 了一些小工具。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">作为一个 AI 资讯时常过载的人，我的刚需之一是要以最快的速度筛选出最有用的新闻。所以我尝试自己做了一个能快速总结信息的浏览器插件（当然是在 Altas 发布之前）。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">其实这个插件我24年就尝试用 Cursor 做，但当时 Cursor 对任务整体的规划能力较弱，经常改了后面忘了前面，陷入“修 bug-产生新 bug”的循环。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">再加上开发一个浏览器插件，需要预先在终端里执行命令安装开发组件。但 Cursor 缺少直接在终端里运行命令的功能，我要反复手动执行安装命令才能顺利 Coding。这个过程说是 Vibe coding，却很难真的 Vibe，没试几次我就放弃了。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">直到2025年 Anthropic 推出了 Claude Code（CC），真的是神器。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">它的第一个厉害之处是用任务拆解和规划能力降低了修 Bug 的难度。我描述需求后，它会先给出一份详细的计划，避免后续改着改着忘记要求，导致反复修 bug。同时，CC 原生具备 CLI 的 Agent 能力，能直接执行终端命令，从创建文件、安装依赖到运行测试都能自动化</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在 CC 的帮助下，我终于开发出了能帮忙迅速翻译、总结的插件。</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6018518518518519\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c49ce8d5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FxVMwH6zrFw64OLutUic6obicqeTsBGGZL3gofdlAzB247pMqAmGXMiawgic48XydBbiawUHYZIxMiakcqD8XqpdQUS4A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6018518518518519\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=aed8dff6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FxVMwH6zrFw64OLutUic6obicqeTsBGGZL388gPcPlDyicZN6IA2ibOAsa3uSwicH9TgVmoTMcx4URdOEMWxIrx2CDwQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: normal;\">*上图：我做的浏览器插件可以对当前网页的内容做结构化的总结；下图：插件还支持用户跟AI就网页内容做进一步的讨论和问答</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">我的日常工作流里还有 AI 硬件。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">针对国内用户正式发布的 AI 录音神器 Plaud 也真正挂在了我身上。它待机时间超长，操作简单（只有一个按键），能一键上传录音内容到 App 进行 AI 转写、总结、导出。对于需要频繁交流的我来说，这种产品免去了跨端操作的繁琐。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">而且它还支持 AI 问答，我能在特定的录音里查询刚刚聊过的问题。这就相当于限定了精准的上下文，能快速给出基本不出错的答案。</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"2.171945701357466\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"442\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=262511a4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FxVMwH6zrFw64OLutUic6obicqeTsBGGZL3ZicaeYbzU7QoUrn6OAPtLPB3WcjQYCpadUsS2mMnxJgB9UnBzaNXX3g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif\"></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">其他一些小功能也很实用，比如用元宝整理微信文章，用飞书知识库查询内部信息等等。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.9916666666666667\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"600\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100008095\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f648f66c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FxVMwH6zrFw64OLutUic6obicqeTsBGGZL3WSBvX5MwjPVsQvxJibRhtpnejmjmokMulWscZkSLibl2Adt50lc8mOUA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: normal;\">*2025年4月元宝上线微信。刚好最近我在关注CES，把链接丢给元宝，它很快就整理出一份特色产品“榜单”。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.75em;text-indent: 0px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">总之，各种 AI 工具已经在2025年彻底渗透进我的日常。甚至我都有点想不起来，之前没有AI的日子是怎么过的。</span></span></p>\n    <div data-pm-slice=\"7 7 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75; box-sizing: border-box; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-align: justify; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); margin-bottom: 0px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">\n     <div>\n      <div>\n       <div>\n        <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 20px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);font-weight: bold;\">02</span></span></strong></p>\n        <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 20px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);font-weight: bold;\">2025年的AI产品：更真实、更易用</span></span></strong></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">从我的变化里不难看出，2025年的 AI 应用，数量和质量都发生了飞跃。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">仔细想想，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">易用感和真实感</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">，大概是2025年 AI 产品们最重要的变化，也是让人们用起来的原因。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">首先是易用。这个维度的体验提升，离不开技术和工程的优化。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">很多人都记得，ChatGPT 刚出现的时候，人们震惊于它流畅的对话能力，但当时的交互也仅限于文字，信息回复既不精准又缺少时效性。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">到了2024年，几乎所有的 AI 助手已经可以联网搜索、进行语音交流和图像理解，交互方式也不限于文字。但当时这些功能都还在初期，输出精准度和意图理解能力都有待提高。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">2025年，两个非常重要的技术变化提升了用户体验。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">第一，深度思考从 DeepSeek 开始成为了各种产品的标配。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">它降低了 AI 产品的幻觉，让内容的可信度更强、更容易被采用。</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5064814814814815\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=24108f0d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FxVMwH6zrFw64OLutUic6obicqeTsBGGZL3wzQsncmupplRrkAZmXXYiaFPNVgBHdiaUeESZjxcvCmPjMyia56yxBe5Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">接着是多模态能力。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">从春天 ChatGPT 的吉卜力画风风靡，再到 Sora 2、NanoBanana 的发布，AI 产品们开始迅速融入各种模态，可玩性显著增强，交互更方便、多样。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal